### GET request all locations
GET http://localhost:7000/locations
Accept: application/json

### GET request all locations from one user
GET http://localhost:7000/users/1/locations
Accept: application/json

### GET request one location from one user
GET http://localhost:7000/users/1/locations/2
Accept: application/json

### Send POST request json body
POST http://localhost:7000/users/2/create
